{"id":623161,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/11/【立此存照】2017-vs-2019对比-没有内容的微博内容/","date":"2019-11-28T16:37:43Z","modified":"2019-11-28T16:37:43Z","title":"【立此存照】2017 VS 2019对比 “没有内容”的微博内容“不宜传播”","content":"<p>近日，“2017到2019的对比挑战”流行网络，据悉该挑战流行于朋友圈，参与者需要po出两张图片与一张&#8221;←2017年 2019→年&#8221;的时间注明图居中，呈现某一事物在两年时间所发生的变化。</p>\n<p>例如：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_623163\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/1574825626469440.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-623163\" class=\"wp-image-623163\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/1574825626469440.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"209\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/1574825626469440.png 512w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/1574825626469440-300x125.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-623163\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"> 有网友表示两年时间自己情感状态发生了变化</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_623164\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/eac58224gy1g9dr52zrpnj20j605574b.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-623164\" class=\"wp-image-623164\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/eac58224gy1g9dr52zrpnj20j605574b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"134\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/eac58224gy1g9dr52zrpnj20j605574b.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/eac58224gy1g9dr52zrpnj20j605574b-300x80.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-623164\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"> 有网友调侃两年时间自己的发量发生了明显变化</p></div>\n<p>而一名微博网友 @狮纳先辈 则po出了一张“颇有内涵”的对比图，这组对比图左侧是2017年新浪微博将用户发布图片审核查删后图片“无法查看”的效果图，而右侧则是2019年改版后新的“查无此图”的新效果。暗讽无论2017还是2019，这样的严厉图片审查一直存在。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cSVAAEewAT.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-623165\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cSVAAEewAT.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cSVAAEewAT.jpeg 639w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cSVAAEewAT-300x258.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这条微博一段时间后就遭到删除，从作者发出的官方解释性回应来看，这条微博被认为“原内容不宜在微博中传播”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cAU4AAM2qt.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-623168\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cAU4AAM2qt.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"373\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cAU4AAM2qt.jpeg 659w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cAU4AAM2qt-300x224.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>该微博作者指出，这是一场颇具讽刺的社会实验，类似那则苏联笑话：“审查者们也在想，你以为别的微博网友不知道你在说什么吗？”而“恶政隐喻不配被转发”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cFVUAAkuQx.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-623169\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cFVUAAkuQx.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"516\" height=\"599\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cFVUAAkuQx.png 516w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKYa4cFVUAAkuQx-258x300.png 258w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 516px) 100vw, 516px\" /></a></p>\n<p>不出意外，这条微博评论又再度被删除，作者最终仅能无奈地表示：</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/截图-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-623170\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/截图-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"507\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/截图-1.png 1062w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/截图-1-296x300.png 296w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/截图-1-1011x1024.png 1011w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/截图-1-768x778.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/截图-1-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1060,"categories":[18271,38895,38912,38921,16848],"tags":[18705,9249,8620,8859,9212]}